Ticket status allow admin to better organize support staff work-flow.Ticket system 
has 4 core status. 
{note}
Ticket status are Open, OnHold,Inprogress & Closed. 
{note}
Core system status for tickets are set to them automatically by the fogpanel ticket
system manager. 
{code}

For example when a customer replied to ticket it is set to "Open", and when admin 
replied to that ticket. That is ticket status is changed to "Answered" status. 
There are 2 additional default status for tickets those are: On Hold & 
In-Progress.
Note:  Active status display all open,onhold,inprogess tickets.

{code}




